main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Okinawa on September 8, 1965, involving circular objects observed for nine minutes.
interesting points: The objects were circular in shape and approximately 45 ft in diameter,They exhibited bluish white coloration and hovered at an altitude of 6000 to 10,000 ft.,Two objects were observed, which faded completely out of sight after the observation.,No photographs are available in the report.,The sightings included other reports from 1 August to 1 September 1965 mentioning lights in the sky.
witness description: military personnel from the 6003rd Support Squadron
